a) ground floor rear extension&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
b) first-floor rear extension&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
c) metal staircase&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: In the interests of the visual amenities of the surrounding area.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
